End-stage liver disease (ESLD) defined by hepatocellular carcinoma (ICD-10 C22.0), hepatic failure (ICD-10 K70.4, K72.1, K72.9), alcoholic liver disease, unspecified (ICD-10 K70.9) and ascites or oesophageal varices (ICD-10 R18, I98.2, I85.0)
Decompensated cirrhosis is defined by all ESLD codes, minus HCC (C 22.0)
